{"ts":"2026-06-26T19:48:01.906Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_end","contentType":"reasoning","reasoning":"**Verifying Package Name**\n\nOkay, great! I've confirmed that `motion/react` is the right package. Now, I'm shifting focus and meticulously double-checking all the required fields for the Proposal Builder intake. I'm making sure I've got a firm grasp of the fields: Organization name (optional), industry, company size, primary challenge and priority outcomes (all required).\n\n\n**Defining Proposal Builder Steps**\n\nI'm now zeroing in on defining the precise steps for the proposal builder to enhance user experience. I've broken the process into four \"Strategic Gateways\" to guide users: \"Profile & Scale\", \"Directives & Challenges\", \"Engagement Strategy & Timeline\", and \"Operational Boundaries & Parameters\". Each gateway will cover specific required and optional fields. For instance, Gateway 1 focuses on organization details, Gateway 2 on challenges and outcomes. I'm focusing on \"Engagement Strategy & Timeline\" and the \"Operational Boundaries & Parameters\". I think the use of selection cards will be useful.\n\n\n**Designing Blueprint Preview**\n\nI'm now focusing on the visual layout. I envision a grid structure with a form on the left for the active gateway and a \"Sovereign AI Proposal Draft Outline\" preview on the right. This preview will dynamically update with org details, proposed SOW sections, and chosen selections like Stakeholder Alignment and Budget Allocation. I'm prioritizing real-time updates and a high-fidelity design to provide an intuitive user experience and show the value of the selections.\n\n\n**Outlining Proposal Sections**\n\nI've got the proposal section structure refined! I've defined sections based on \"Factory\" or \"Operate\" selections within the \"Engagement Strategy & Timeline\" gateway. \"Factory\" leads to \"Multi-Agent Fleet Modeling & Scale\" and \"Custom Agent Training\". \"Operate\" triggers \"Day-2 Sovereign Operation\" and \"SLA Monitoring.\" I'm implementing a real-time verification checklist that includes profile parameters, challenge identification, engagement path, and timeline confirmation. I also want a telemetry indicator for compliance metrics, ideally a sparkline or a visual indicator for things like security compliance and data retention. Now I will focus on implementing this in `app/build/proposal/page.tsx`.\n\n\n**Defining Strategic Domains**\n\nI'm now detailing industry options to ensure a technical and strategic feel. I'm focusing on providing options such as Finance, Healthcare, Energy, Public Sector, Telecom, and Retail, each described with high-level technical application examples. Then I need to flesh out company size choices, along with the primary challenges that correspond to the choices. I will work on connecting them to the overall framework.\n\n\n**Defining Project Outcomes**\n\nI'm now focusing on specific priority outcomes for the proposal builder, specifically around data residency and system security. I'm prioritizing outcomes such as sub-150ms agent latency, 100% on-premise isolation, continuous AI drift guard, and accelerated deployment within six weeks. The engagement paths now include Garage, Foundry, Factory, and Operate. I am working on how to incorporate them into the model, and how they will correspond to the selections available to the user.\n\n\n**Refining Engagement Options**\n\nOkay, I've got a clearer picture of the engagement paths. I've defined **GFF Factory** for agent fleet ingestion and fine-tuning, **GFF Operate** for managed sovereignty, and the single-tenant VPC for delivery. I'm also now focusing on refining the tactical, strategic, and transformational timelines to improve clarity. Then I want to define budget ranges, geographies, and stakeholder types as optional parameters. Finally, I'll transition into thinking about how the builder will transition to the \"Compiled SOW & Proposal\" screen.\n\n\n**Visualizing Compilation Process**\n\nI'm now focusing on the user experience after a user clicks \"Sovereign Compile.\" I'm envisioning a sleek compilation animation with scrolling console logs to build anticipation. I'll include things like secure handshake verification, challenge matrix resolution, and template ingestion. Then, the animation smoothly transitions into the \"Compiled SOW Folder,\" a results dashboard with tabs, including a strategy & alignment tab and a technical topology & SLA tab.\n\n\n\n**Visualizing Download Options**\n\nI'm now focusing on the final \"Compiled SOW Folder\" experience, designing the action hub. I'm prioritizing dynamic SOW breakdowns with phase specs and interactive bullet lists. I'm also ensuring a professional summary table for commercial details. Finally, I'm incorporating secure verification seals and dynamic download cards for artifacts with slick micro-interactions for download progress.\n\n\n**Constructing UI Code**\n\nI'm now writing out the page structure, and I am focused on premium and strategic design. I am going to focus on an amazing interface with components. The code will utilize standard Next.js React with hooks. I am beginning the development of `app/build/proposal/page.tsx` and verifying it. I will ensure all fields are interactive with state management, layout, validation, and graphics for a compile mode and dynamic results mode with excellent mobile support.\n\n\n**Confirming Feature Set**\n\nOkay, I've confirmed the feature set! I'm now making sure I'm implementing all the required elements. I will be incorporating all of the required fields. I am using local state and validation. I will not be generating real documents. I'm focusing on making the UI feel like an enterprise proposal studio with guided forms, live outline preview, engagement path cards, and a clean summary panel. I will be using subtle motion, polished cards, and mobile-friendly layouts. I am also making sure I run the lint and build checks.\n\n\n**Defining Form Fields**\n\nI'm now detailing the form fields, like organization name, industry, company size, primary challenge, and priority outcomes. I've also defined engagement paths, target timelines, and optional parameters such as budget ranges, geographies, and stakeholder types. Now I'm carefully structuring the code to handle these fields effectively, ensuring proper data types and validation, and considering all the details.\n\n\n**Implementing Validation Checks**\n\nI'm now focusing on implementing validation checks to ensure all required fields are complete before compilation. I want to add a beautiful warning for skipped steps. I'm also going to create a premium, interactive UI with custom SVG diagrams, including an Agent Workflow Map and Technical Topology diagram. I will create gorgeous SVG icons for the Engagement Path cards with subtle hover micro-interactions.\n\n\n"}}
{"ts":"2026-06-26T19:48:01.910Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"tool","toolName":"editor","toolCallId":"a31nwqw6","input":{"path":"/Users/ayushbansal/Documents/GitHub/hirezapp_landing_page/app/build/proposal/page.tsx","old_text":null,"new_text":"\"use client\";\n\nimport React, { useState, useEffect } from \"react\";\nimport { motion, AnimatePresence } from \"motion/react\";\nimport { ToolPageShell, ToolCTA } from \"@/components/build/components\";\n\n// ============================================================================\n// Types & Interface Definitions\n// ============================================================================\nexport interface ProposalInputs {\n  organizationName: string;\n  industry: string;\n  companySize: string;\n  primaryChallenge: string;\n  priorityOutcomes: string[];\n  preferredEngagementPath: string;\n  targetTimeline: string;\n  budgetRange: string;\n  geography: string;\n  stakeholders: string[];\n}\n\nconst INITIAL_DATA: ProposalInputs = {\n  organizationName: \"\",\n  industry: \"\",\n  companySize: \"\",\n  primaryChallenge: \"\",\n  priorityOutcomes: [],\n  preferredEngagementPath: \"\",\n  targetTimeline: \"\",\n  budgetRange: \"\",\n  geography: \"\",\n  stakeholders: [],\n};\n\n// ============================================================================\n// Constants and Options\n// ============================================================================\nconst INDUSTRIES = [\n  { id: \"banking\", title: \"Banking & Financial Services\", description: \"Sovereign ledger reconciliation, high-throughput multi-agent auditing.\", icon: \"🏛️\" },\n  { id: \"healthcare\", title: \"Healthcare & Life Sciences\", description: \"HIPAA-protected air-gapped clinical trials, zero-persistence PHI nodes.\", icon: \"🔬\" },\n  { id: \"energy\", title: \"Energy & Infrastructure\", description: \"Critical edge grid telemetry security, proactive risk mitigation.\", icon: \"⚡\" },\n  { id: \"public-sector\", title: \"Public Sector & Defense\", description: \"Strict sovereign compliance, localized network enclaves, FedRAMP alignment.\", icon: \"🛡️\" },\n  { id: \"telecom\", title: \"Telecom & Networks\", description: \"Ultra-low latency signaling, intelligent high-capacity multi-agent routing.\", icon: \"📡\" },\n  { id: \"retail\", title: \"Retail & Supply Chain\", description: \"Edge orchestrator pipelines, intelligent inventory synchronization nodes.\", icon: \"📦\" }\n];\n\nconst COMPANY_SIZES = [\n  { id: \"mid-market\", title: \"Growth Enterprise\", desc: \"500 - 2,000 headcount. Focused on local enclaves.\", limit: \"Strategic Incubation Tier\" },\n  { id: \"enterprise\", title: \"Core Enterprise\", desc: \"2,000 - 10,000 headcount. Single-tenant dedicated VPC.\", limit: \"Global Enterprise Tier\" },\n  { id: \"conglomerate\", title: \"Global Sovereign Scale\", desc: \"10,000+ headcount. Multi-region decentralized nodes.\", limit: \"Sovereign Consensus Tier\" }\n];\n\nconst CHALLENGES = [\n  { id: \"orchestration_lag\", title: \"Multi-System Orchestration Lag\", desc: \"Legacy APIs causing system desynchronization and operational blind spots.\" },\n  { id: \"sovereign_boundary\", title: \"Sovereign Compliance Barriers\", desc: \"Strict jurisdictional data regulations requiring strict zero-cloud-retention.\" },\n  { id: \"drift_deficits\", title: \"Model Drift & Safety Deficits\", desc: \"Autonomous execution lines deviating from strategic guidelines over time.\" },\n  { id: \"friction_enclaves\", title: \"Infrastructural Onboarding Friction\", desc: \"Slow environment setup and manual verification of secure isolated enclaves.\" }\n];\n\nconst OUTCOMES = [\n  { id: \"latency_cut\", title: \"Sub-150ms Agent Latency\", desc: \"Enable instantaneous execution pathways across enterprise system barriers.\" },\n  { id: \"vpc_isolation\", title: \"100% Air-Gapped VPC Isolation\", desc: \"Enforce complete data encapsulation inside dedicated tenant memory boundaries.\" },\n  { id: \"drift_guard\", title: \"Continuous Guardrails & Audits\", desc: \"Cryptographically lock behavior rules to prevent operational model drift.\" },\n  { id: \"speed_deploy\", title: \"Accelerated Deployment (< 6 Weeks)\", desc: \"Spin up production-ready autonomous nodes with Zero-Persistence pipelines.\" }\n];\n\nconst ENGAGEMENT_PATHS = [\n  {\n    id: \"Garage\",\n    title: \"GFF Garage\",\n    tagline: \"Strategic Co-Design Enclave\",\n    description: \"Collaborative strategy sprint. We map your topologies and deploy an isolated sandbox prototype in under 4 weeks.\",\n    duration: \"4 Weeks\",\n    color: \"#009DFF\",\n    borderGlow: \"hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(0,157,255,0.15)]\",\n    bgClass: \"bg-blue-500/5\",\n    icon: (\n      <svg className=\"w-5 h-5 text-[#009DFF]\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\">\n        <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" strokeWidth={1.5} d=\"M11 5H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v11a2 2 0 002 2h11a2 2 0 002-2v-5m-1.414-9.414a2 2 0 112.828 2.828L11.828 15H9v-2.828l8.586-8.586z\" />\n      </svg>\n    )\n  },\n  {\n    id: \"Foundry\",\n    title: \"GFF Foundry\",\n    tagline: \"Core Platform Ingestion\",\n    description: \"Our core engineering engagement. Deploy our secure multi-agent orchestrator and vector grids inside your VPC in 8-12 weeks.\",\n    duration: \"8-12 Weeks\",\n    color: \"#9D00FF\",\n    borderGlow: \"hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(157,0,255,0.15)]\",\n    bgClass: \"bg-purple-500/5\",\n    icon: (\n      <svg className=\"w-5 h-5 text-[#9D00FF]\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\">\n        <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" strokeWidth={1.5} d=\"M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z\" />\n      </svg>\n    )\n  },\n  {\n    id: \"Factory\",\n    title: \"GFF Factory\",\n    tagline: \"Massive Agent Industrialization\",\n    description: \"Industrial-scale execution. We customize, fine-tune, and roll out dozens of specialized cognitive nodes tailored to complex processes.\",\n    duration: \"12-16 Weeks\",\n    color: \"#00FF9D\",\n    borderGlow: \"hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(0,255,157,0.15)]\",\n    bgClass: \"bg-emerald-500/5\",\n    icon: (\n      <svg className=\"w-5 h-5 text-[#00FF9D]\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\">\n        <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" strokeWidth={1.5} d=\"M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10\" />\n      </svg>\n    )\n  },\n  {\n    id: \"Operate\",\n    title: \"GFF Operate\",\n    tagline: \"Hardened SecOps & Management\",\n    description: \"Persistent Day-2 managed sovereignty. Continual security telemetry updates, custom model drift patches, and dedicated audit nodes.\",\n    duration: \"Ongoing SLA\",\n    color: \"#E4000F\",\n    borderGlow: \"hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(228,0,15,0.15)]\",\n    bgClass: \"bg-red-500/5\",\n    icon: (\n      <svg className=\"w-5 h-5 text-[#E4000F]\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\">\n        <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" strokeWidth={1.5} d=\"M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z\" />\n      </svg>\n    )\n  }\n];\n\nconst TIMELINES = [\n  { id: \"immediate\", title: \"Immediate Acceleration\", desc: \"Targeting launch within 1 - 3 months for high-priority enclaves.\" },\n  { id: \"strategic\", title: \"Strategic Integration\", desc: \"Unified multi-system integration targeting a 3 - 6 month horizon.\" },\n  { id: \"transformational\", title: \"Transformational Horizon\", desc: \"Comprehensive enterprise shift with deep compliance structures over 6 - 12 months.\" }\n];\n\nconst BUDGETS = [\n  { id: \"tier1\", title: \"Strategic Discovery\", desc: \"Focus on validation sprints & isolated sandboxes. (Under $250k)\" },\n  { id: \"tier2\", title: \"Production Deployment\", desc: \"Core VPC infrastructure & multi-agent mesh setup. ($250k - $1M)\" },\n  { id: \"tier3\", title: \"Industrial Enterprise\", desc: \"Multi-department agent scaling and complex custom DAG models. ($1M - $5M)\" },\n  { id: \"tier4\", title: \"Sovereign Infrastructure\", desc: \"Global sovereign nodes, custom model weights, multi-region SLAs. ($5M+)\" }\n];\n\nconst GEOGRAPHIES = [\n  { id: \"na\", title: \"North America\", sub: \"US / Canada sovereign VPC zones\" },\n  { id: \"eu\", title: \"European Union\", sub: \"Strict GDPR-compliant isolated nodes\" },\n  { id: \"apac\", title: \"Asia-Pacific\", sub: \"APAC Regional data center hubs\" },\n  { id: \"global\", title: \"Decentralized Sovereign\", sub: \"Multi-jurisdictional compliant mesh\" }\n];\n\nconst STAKEHOLDERS = [\n  { id: \"board\", title: \"Board of Directors\", role: \"Sovereign ROI & Governance oversight\" },\n  { id: \"cto_cio\", title: \"Office of CIO / CTO\", role: \"Integrations, API security, and hardware parameters\" },\n  { id: \"compliance\", title: \"Security & Compliance Council\", role: \"VPC rules, SOC2 guarantees, data air-gaps\" },\n  { id: \"business_lead\", title: \"LOB Business Executives\", role: \"Workflow efficiency gains and daily business velocity\" }\n];\n\n// ============================================================================\n// Core Page Component\n// ============================================================================\nexport default function ProposalStudioPage() {\n  const [data, setData] = useState<ProposalInputs>(INITIAL_DATA);\n  const [activeStep, setActiveStep] = useState<number>(0);\n  const [error, setError] = useState<string | null>(null);\n  \n  // App States: \"edit\" | \"compiling\" | \"completed\"\n  const [appState, setAppState] = useState<\"edit\" | \"compiling\" | \"completed\">(\"edit\");\n  const [compilingLogIndex, setCompilingLogIndex] = useState<number>(0);\n  const [compiledResult, setCompiledResult] = useState<any>(null);\n\n  // Active SOW Document Tab: \"summary\" | \"topology\" | \"sow\" | \"commercials\"\n  const [activeTab, setActiveTab] = useState<string>(\"summary\");\n\n  // Simulated download triggers\n  const [downloadProgress, setDownloadProgress] = useState<Record<string, number>>({});\n  const [downloadSuccess, setDownloadSuccess] = useState<Record<string, boolean>>({});\n\n  // Compile Logging Timeline\n  const COMPILING_LOGS = [\n    { text: \"Initializing GFF Sovereign Proposal Compiler v4.26...\", delay: 400 },\n    { text: \"Ingesting organizational variables & industry taxonomy...\", delay: 500 },\n    { text: \"Verifying network containment filters & single-tenant boundaries...\", delay: 600 },\n    { text: \"Synthesizing customized Statement of Work (SOW) chapters...\", delay: 500 },\n    { text: \"Evaluating priority challenges against GFF Node execution DAGs...\", delay: 600 },\n    { text: \"Securing blueprint with cryptographic hash validation...\", delay: 400 },\n    { text: \"Compiling strategic executive Briefing and topological specs...\", delay: 300 }\n  ];\n\n  useEffect(() => {\n    if (appState !== \"compiling\") return;\n\n    if (compilingLogIndex < COMPILING_LOGS.length) {\n      const timer = setTimeout(() => {\n        setCompilingLogIndex((prev) => prev + 1);\n      }, COMPILING_LOGS[compilingLogIndex].delay);\n      return () => clearTimeout(timer);\n    } else {\n      // Completed compiling. Generate mock SOW data based on selections.\n      setCompiledResult({\n        hash: `SHA-256: 0x${Array.from({ length: 40 }, () => Math.floor(Math.random() * 16).toString(16)).join(\"\")}`,\n        compiledAt: new Date().toLocaleString(),\n        revisionId: `REV-${Math.floor(100000 + Math.random() * 900000)}`,\n        estimatedCost: data.budgetRange \n          ? BUDGETS.find(b => b.id === data.budgetRange)?.title.split(\".\")[1] || \"$150,000 - $400,000 / Year\"\n          : \"$250,000 - $600,000 / Year\",\n        slaGuarantee: data.industry === \"healthcare\" ? \"99.99% PHI Isolation SLA\" : data.industry === \"banking\" ? \"99.999% Atomic Consensus SLA\" : \"99.9% Uptime SLA\"\n      });\n      setAppState(\"completed\");\n    }\n  }, [appState, compilingLogIndex]);\n\n  // Validations per step\n  const validateStep = (step: number): boolean => {\n    setError(null);\n    if (step === 0) {\n      if (!data.industry) {\n        setError(\"Strategic Domain (Industry) selection is required.\");\n        return false;\n      }\n      if (!data.companySize) {\n        setError(\"Company Scale parameter is required.\");\n        return false;\n      }\n    } else if (step === 1) {\n      if (!data.primaryChallenge) {\n        setError(\"A primary operational challenge must be specified.\");\n        return false;\n      }\n      if (data.priorityOutcomes.length === 0) {\n        setError(\"At least one strategic priority outcome must be selected.\");\n        return false;\n      }\n    } else if (step === 2) {\n      if (!data.preferredEngagementPath) {\n        setError(\"An engagement model path is required.\");\n        return false;\n      }\n      if (!data.targetTimeline) {\n        setError(\"Target implementation timeline is required.\");\n        return false;\n      }\n    }\n    return true;\n  };\n\n  const handleNext = () => {\n    if (validateStep(activeStep)) {\n      if (activeStep < 3) {\n        setActiveStep((prev) => prev + 1);\n      } else {\n        // Trigger compile\n        setCompilingLogIndex(0);\n        setAppState(\"compiling\");\n      }\n    }\n  };\n\n  const handleBack = () => {\n    setError(null);\n    if (activeStep > 0) {\n      setActiveStep((prev) => prev - 1);\n    }\n  };\n\n  const handleReset = () => {\n    setData(INITIAL_DATA);\n    setActiveStep(0);\n    setError(null);\n    setAppState(\"edit\");\n    setDownloadProgress({});\n    setDownloadSuccess({});\n    setActiveTab(\"summary\");\n  };\n\n  const toggleOutcome = (id: string) => {\n    setData((prev) => {\n      const exists = prev.priorityOutcomes.includes(id);\n      return {\n        ...prev,\n        priorityOutcomes: exists\n          ? prev.priorityOutcomes.filter((item) => item !== id)\n          : [...prev.priorityOutcomes, id]\n      };\n    });\n  };\n\n  const toggleStakeholder = (id: string) => {\n    setData((prev) => {\n      const exists = prev.stakeholders.includes(id);\n      return {\n        ...prev,\n        stakeholders: exists\n          ? prev.stakeholders.filter((item) => item !== id)\n          : [...prev.stakeholders, id]\n      };\n    });\n  };\n\n  // Simulated Download Action with custom visual state\n  const triggerDownload = (fileName: string) => {\n    if (downloadProgress[fileName] !== undefined) return;\n\n    setDownloadProgress(prev => ({ ...prev, [fileName]: 0 }));\n    setDownloadSuccess(prev => ({ ...prev, [fileName]: false }));\n\n    const interval = setInterval(() => {\n      setDownloadProgress(prev => {\n        const current = prev[fileName] || 0;\n        if (current >= 100) {\n          clearInterval(interval);\n          setDownloadSuccess(s => ({ ...s, [fileName]: true }));\n          return prev;\n        }\n        return { ...prev, [fileName]: current + 25 };\n      });\n    }, 200);\n  };\n\n  return (\n    <ToolPageShell showContact={appState !== \"completed\"}>\n      {/* ----------------- SUB-HEADER / TOP PROGRESS BAR ----------------- */}\n      <div className=\"mb-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center justify-between gap-4 border-b border-white/5 pb-6\">\n        <div>\n          <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest block\">\n            Phase 3 Strategic Interface\n          </span>\n          <h1 className=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tight\">\n            Sovereign SOW <span className=\"text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-white to-white/50\">Proposal Studio</span>\n          </h1>\n          <p className=\"text-white/40 text-xs mt-1 max-w-xl font-light\">\n            Dynamically model customized GFF AI agent architectures, timelines, and formal Statement of Work outlines.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n\n        {appState === \"edit\" && (\n          <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2 bg-[#08080c] border border-white/5 px-4 py-2.5 rounded-xl font-mono text-[10px]\">\n            <span className=\"text-white/30 uppercase mr-1\">Design Gates:</span>\n            {[0, 1, 2, 3].map((step) => {\n              const isActive = activeStep === step;\n              const isCompleted = activeStep > step;\n              return (\n                <div key={step} className=\"flex items-center\">\n                  <div\n                    onClick={() => { if (isCompleted || step < activeStep) setActiveStep(step); }}\n                    className={`w-5 h-5 rounded flex items-center justify-center font-bold transition-all cursor-pointer ${\n                      isActive \n                        ? \"bg-[#009DFF] text-black shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(0,157,255,0.4)]\" \n                        : isCompleted \n                        ? \"bg-[#00FF9D]/15 text-[#00FF9D] border border-[#00FF9D]/30\" \n                        : \"border border-white/10 text-white/30\"\n                    }`}\n                  >\n                    {isCompleted ? \"✓\" : step + 1}\n                  </div>\n                  {step < 3 && <div className={`w-3 h-px ${isCompleted ? \"bg-[#00FF9D]/30\" : \"bg-white/10\"}`} />}\n                </div>\n              );\n            })}\n          </div>\n        )}\n\n        {appState === \"completed\" && (\n          <button\n            onClick={handleReset}\n            className=\"px-4 py-2 rounded-lg border border-white/10 hover:bg-white/5 text-xs text-white/80 font-mono flex items-center gap-2 transition-colors\"\n          >\n            <svg className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\">\n              <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" strokeWidth={2} d=\"M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 1121.21 15H18\" />\n            </svg>\n            <span>NEW OUTLINE SPEC</span>\n          </button>\n        )}\n      </div>\n\n      {/* ------------------------------------------------------------------\n          STATE 1: STRATEGIC GUIDED INTAKE FORM\n          ------------------------------------------------------------------ */}\n      {appState === \"edit\" && (\n        <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-start\">\n          \n          {/* LEFT COL: STRATEGIC FORMS (GATEWAYS) */}\n          <div className=\"lg:col-span-7 space-y-6\">\n            <div className=\"bg-[#030306]/85 border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8 min-h-[480px] flex flex-col justify-between relative overflow-hidden backdrop-blur-xl\">\n              <div className=\"absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-[#009DFF]/2 pointer-events-none blur-2xl rounded-full\" />\n              \n              <div className=\"space-y-6\">\n                {/* Gateway Identifier */}\n                <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between border-b border-white/5 pb-4\">\n                  <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-[#009DFF]/10 text-[#009DFF] border border-[#009DFF]/20 uppercase tracking-wider font-bold\">\n                    Gate {activeStep + 1} of 4: {activeStep === 0 ? \"Profile & Scale\" : activeStep === 1 ? \"Directives & Challenges\" : activeStep === 2 ? \"Engagement Path\" : \"Operational Boundaries\"}\n                  </span>\n                  <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/30\">VPC BOUNDARY SECURED</span>\n                </div>\n\n                {/* STEP 1: PROFILE & SCALE */}\n                {activeStep === 0 && (\n                  <div className=\"space-y-6 animate-fadeIn\">\n                    <div>\n                      <label className=\"block text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2\">\n                        Organization Name (Optional)\n                      </label>\n                      <input\n                        type=\"text\"\n                        placeholder=\"e.g. Apex Global Operations\"\n                        value={data.organizationName}\n                        onChange={(e) => setData({ ...data, organizationName: e.target.value })}\n                        className=\"w-full h-11 bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/10 rounded-lg px-4 text-xs text-white placeholder-white/20 focus:outline-none focus:border-[#009DFF]/50 transition-colors\"\n                      />\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div className=\"space-y-3\">\n                      <label className=\"block text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase tracking-wider\">\n                        Strategic Industry Domain <span className=\"text-[#E4000F]\">*</span>\n                      </label>\n                      <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3\">\n                        {INDUSTRIES.map((ind) => {\n                          const isSelected = data.industry === ind.id;\n                          return (\n                            <button\n                              key={ind.id}\n                              type=\"button\"\n                              onClick={() => setData({ ...data, industry: ind.id })}\n                              className={`p-4 rounded-xl border text-left transition-all duration-200 group relative flex flex-col justify-between h-28 ${\n                                isSelected \n                                  ? \"border-[#009DFF] bg-[#009DFF]/5 shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(0,157,255,0.08)]\" \n                                  : \"border-white/5 bg-[#030304] hover:border-white/10 hover:bg-white/[0.01]\"\n                              }`}\n                            >\n                              <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between w-full\">\n                                <span className=\"text-lg\">{ind.icon}</span>\n                                {isSelected && (\n                                  <span className=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#009DFF]\" />\n                                )}\n                              </div>\n                              <div>\n                                <h4 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white group-hover:text-white/90 transition-colors\">{ind.title}</h4>\n                                <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/45 leading-tight font-light mt-1 line-clamp-1\">{ind.description}</p>\n                              </div>\n                            </button>\n                          );\n                        })}\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div className=\"space-y-3\">\n                      <label className=\"block text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase tracking-wider\">\n                        Deployment Scale & Complexity <span className=\"text-[#E4000F]\">*</span>\n                      </label>\n                      <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-3\">\n                        {COMPANY_SIZES.map((sz) => {\n                          const isSelected = data.companySize === sz.id;\n                          return (\n                            <button\n                              key={sz.id}\n                              type=\"button\"\n                              onClick={() => setData({ ...data, companySize: sz.id })}\n                              className={`p-4 rounded-xl border text-left transition-all duration-200 group h-24 flex flex-col justify-between ${\n                                isSelected \n                                  ? \"border-[#009DFF] bg-[#009DFF]/5 shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(0,157,255,0.08)]\" \n                                  : \"border-white/5 bg-[#030304] hover:border-white/10\"\n                              }`}\n                            >\n                              <div>\n                                <h4 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white\">{sz.title}</h4>\n                                <p className=\"text-[9px] text-white/40 mt-1\">{sz.desc}</p>\n                              </div>\n                              <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] uppercase tracking-wider\">{sz.limit}</span>\n                            </button>\n                          );\n                        })}\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                )}\n\n                {/* STEP 2: DIRECTIVES & CHALLENGES */}\n                {activeStep === 1 && (\n                  <div className=\"space-y-6 animate-fadeIn\">\n                    <div className=\"space-y-3\">\n                      <label className=\"block text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase tracking-wider\">\n                        Primary Operational Challenge <span className=\"text-[#E4000F]\">*</span>\n                      </label>\n                      <div className=\"space-y-2.5\">\n                        {CHALLENGES.map((ch) => {\n                          const isSelected = data.primaryChallenge === ch.id;\n                          return (\n                            <button\n                              key={ch.id}\n                              type=\"button\"\n                              onClick={() => setData({ ...data, primaryChallenge: ch.id })}\n                              className={`w-full p-4 rounded-xl border text-left transition-all duration-200 flex items-start gap-4 ${\n                                isSelected \n                                  ? \"border-[#009DFF] bg-[#009DFF]/5\" \n                                  : \"border-white/5 bg-[#030304] hover:border-white/10\"\n                              }`}\n                            >\n                              <div className={`w-4 h-4 rounded-full border flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5 shrink-0 transition-colors ${\n                                isSelected ? \"border-[#009DFF]\" : \"border-white/20\"\n                              }`}>\n                                {isSelected && <div className=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#009DFF]\" />}\n                              </div>\n                              <div>\n                                <h4 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white\">{ch.title}</h4>\n                                <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/45 mt-1 font-light leading-relaxed\">{ch.desc}</p>\n                              </div>\n                            </button>\n                          );\n                        })}\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div className=\"space-y-3\">\n                      <div className=\"flex justify-between items-baseline\">\n                        <label className=\"block text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase tracking-wider\">\n                          Priority Strategic Outcomes <span className=\"text-[#E4000F]\">*</span>\n                        </label>\n                        <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/20\">MULTI-SELECT</span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3\">\n                        {OUTCOMES.map((out) => {\n                          const isSelected = data.priorityOutcomes.includes(out.id);\n                          return (\n                            <button\n                              key={out.id}\n                              type=\"button\"\n                              onClick={() => toggleOutcome(out.id)}\n                              className={`p-4 rounded-xl border text-left transition-all duration-200 group flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[100px] ${\n                                isSelected \n                                  ? \"border-[#00FF9D] bg-[#00FF9D]/5\" \n                                  : \"border-white/5 bg-[#030304] hover:border-white/10\"\n                              }`}\n                            >\n                              <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between w-full\">\n                                <h4 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white\">{out.title}</h4>\n                                <div className={`w-3.5 h-3.5 rounded border transition-colors flex items-center justify-center ${\n                                  isSelected ? \"border-[#00FF9D] bg-[#00FF9D] text-black\" : \"border-white/20\"\n                                }`}>\n                                  {isSelected && <span className=\"text-[9px] font-black leading-none\">✓</span>}\n                                </div>\n                              </div>\n                              <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/45 mt-2 font-light leading-tight\">{out.desc}</p>\n                            </button>\n                          );\n                        })}\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                )}\n\n                {/* STEP 3: PREFERRED ENGAGEMENT PATH & TIMELINE */}\n                {activeStep === 2 && (\n                  <div className=\"space-y-6 animate-fadeIn\">\n                    <div className=\"space-y-3\">\n                      <label className=\"block text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase tracking-wider\">\n                        Preferred GFF Engagement Model <span className=\"text-[#E4000F]\">*</span>\n                      </label>\n                      \n                      <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3\">\n                        {ENGAGEMENT_PATHS.map((path) => {\n                          const isSelected = data.preferredEngagementPath === path.id;\n                          return (\n                            <button\n                              key={path.id}\n                              type=\"button\"\n                              onClick={() => setData({ ...data, preferredEngagementPath: path.id })}\n                              className={`p-5 rounded-2xl border text-left transition-all duration-300 relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[180px] ${\n                                isSelected \n                                  ? \"bg-white/[0.02]\" \n                                  : \"border-white/5 bg-[#030304]/80\"\n                              } ${path.borderGlow}`}\n                              style={isSelected ? { borderColor: path.color } : undefined}\n                            >\n                              {/* Selection overlay background */}\n                              {isSelected && (\n                                <div className=\"absolute inset-0 opacity-10 pointer-events-none transition-opacity\" style={{ backgroundColor: path.color }} />\n                              )}\n                              \n                              <div className=\"space-y-3\">\n                                <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center\">\n                                  <div className=\"p-2 rounded-lg bg-white/5 border border-white/10\">\n                                    {path.icon}\n                                  </div>\n                                  <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono font-bold tracking-widest uppercase px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-white/5 text-white/80\">\n                                    {path.duration}\n                                  </span>\n                                </div>\n                                <div>\n                                  <h3 className=\"text-xs font-black text-white\">{path.title}</h3>\n                                  <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono block opacity-50 font-light mt-0.5\">{path.tagline}</span>\n                                </div>\n                                <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/50 leading-relaxed font-light\">{path.description}</p>\n                              </div>\n\n                              {isSelected && (\n                                <div className=\"mt-4 flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[9px] font-mono font-bold uppercase\" style={{ color: path.color }}>\n                                  <span className=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full animate-ping\" style={{ backgroundColor: path.color }} />\n                                  <span>Selected Path</span>\n                                </div>\n                              )}\n                            </button>\n                          );\n                        })}\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div className=\"space-y-3\">\n                      <label className=\"block text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase tracking-wider\">\n                        Target Implementation Timeline <span className=\"text-[#E4000F]\">*</span>\n                      </label>\n                      <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-3\">\n                        {TIMELINES.map((tm) => {\n                          const isSelected = data.targetTimeline === tm.id;\n                          return (\n                            <button\n                              key={tm.id}\n                              type=\"button\"\n                              onClick={() => setData({ ...data, targetTimeline: tm.id })}\n                              className={`p-4 rounded-xl border text-left transition-all duration-200 flex flex-col justify-between h-24 ${\n                                isSelected \n                                  ? \"border-[#009DFF] bg-[#009DFF]/5\" \n                                  : \"border-white/5 bg-[#030304] hover:border-white/10\"\n                              }`}\n                            >\n                              <h4 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white leading-tight\">{tm.title}</h4>\n                              <p className=\"text-[9px] text-white/40 mt-1 leading-tight font-light line-clamp-2\">{tm.desc}</p>\n                            </button>\n                          );\n                        })}\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                )}\n\n                {/* STEP 4: PARAMETERS (OPTIONAL FIELDS) */}\n                {activeStep === 3 && (\n                  <div className=\"space-y-6 animate-fadeIn\">\n                    <div className=\"space-y-3\">\n                      <div className=\"flex justify-between items-baseline\">\n                        <label className=\"block text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase tracking-wider\">\n                          Corporate Budget Range Allocation (Optional)\n                        </label>\n                        <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-[#00FF9D]\">ENCLAVE ENCRYPTED</span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3\">\n                        {BUDGETS.map((bg) => {\n                          const isSelected = data.budgetRange === bg.id;\n                          return (\n                            <button\n                              key={bg.id}\n                              type=\"button\"\n                              onClick={() => setData({ ...data, budgetRange: bg.id })}\n                              className={`p-4 rounded-xl border text-left transition-all duration-200 flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[85px] ${\n                                isSelected \n                                  ? \"border-[#00FF9D] bg-[#00FF9D]/5\" \n                                  : \"border-white/5 bg-[#030304] hover:border-white/10\"\n                              }`}\n                            >\n                              <h4 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white\">{bg.title}</h4>\n                              <p className=\"text-[9px] text-white/40 mt-1 font-light leading-normal\">{bg.desc}</p>\n                            </button>\n                          );\n                        })}\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6\">\n                      <div className=\"space-y-3\">\n                        <label className=\"block text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase tracking-wider\">\n                          Deployment Geography (Optional)\n                        </label>\n                        <div className=\"relative\">\n                          <select\n                            value={data.geography}\n                            onChange={(e) => setData({ ...data, geography: e.target.value })}\n                            className=\"w-full h-11 bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/10 rounded-lg px-4 text-xs text-white placeholder-white/20 focus:outline-none focus:border-[#009DFF]/50 appearance-none cursor-pointer transition-colors\"\n                          >\n                            <option value=\"\" className=\"bg-[#030306]\">-- Select Target Zone --</option>\n                            {GEOGRAPHIES.map((geo) => (\n                              <option key={geo.id} value={geo.id} className=\"bg-[#030306] text-white\">\n                                {geo.title} ({geo.sub})\n                              </option>\n                            ))}\n                          </select>\n                          <div className=\"absolute top-1/2 right-3.5 -translate-y-1/2 pointer-events-none text-white/30 text-[10px]\">\n                            ▼\n                          </div>\n                        </div>\n                      </div>\n\n                      <div className=\"space-y-3\">\n                        <div className=\"flex justify-between items-baseline\">\n                          <label className=\"block text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase tracking-wider\">\n                            Stakeholder Alignment (Optional)\n                          </label>\n                          <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-white/20\">MULTI-SELECT</span>\n                        </div>\n                        <div className=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\">\n                          {STAKEHOLDERS.map((st) => {\n                            const isSelected = data.stakeholders.includes(st.id);\n                            return (\n                              <button\n                                key={st.id}\n                                type=\"button\"\n                                onClick={() => toggleStakeholder(st.id)}\n                                className={`h-8 px-3 rounded-full border text-[10px] font-mono uppercase tracking-wider transition-all duration-200 ${\n                                  isSelected \n                                    ? \"bg-[#009DFF]/15 border-[#009DFF] text-[#009DFF]\" \n                                    : \"bg-white/5 border-white/5 text-white/50 hover:border-white/10\"\n                                }`}\n                              >\n                                {st.title}\n                              </button>\n                            );\n                          })}\n                        </div>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                )}\n              </div>\n\n              {/* ACTION FOOTER */}\n              <div className=\"space-y-4 border-t border-white/5 pt-6 mt-8\">\n                {error && (\n                  <div className=\"p-3.5 rounded-xl bg-[#E4000F]/5 border border-[#E4000F]/15 flex gap-2.5 text-xs text-white/80 animate-headShake\">\n                    <span className=\"text-[#E4000F] font-bold font-mono\">WARNING:</span>\n                    <p>{error}</p>\n                  </div>\n                )}\n                \n                <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center gap-4\">\n                  <button\n                    type=\"button\"\n                    onClick={handleBack}\n                    disabled={activeStep === 0}\n                    className={`px-5 h-10 rounded-lg border text-xs font-semibold uppercase flex items-center gap-2 transition-all ${\n                      activeStep === 0 \n                        ? \"border-white/5 text-white/10 cursor-not-allowed\" \n                        : \"border-white/10 text-white hover:bg-white/5\"\n                    }`}\n                  >\n                    Back\n                  </button>\n                  \n                  {activeStep > 0 && (\n                    <button\n                      type=\"button\"\n                      onClick={handleReset}\n                      className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/30 hover:text-white transition-colors uppercase\"\n                    >\n                      [Reset Draft]\n                    </button>\n                  )}\n                  \n                  <button\n                    type=\"button\"\n                    onClick={handleNext}\n                    className=\"px-6 h-10 rounded-lg text-xs font-bold uppercase bg-[#009DFF] text-black hover:bg-[#009DFF]/90 font-mono shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(0,157,255,0.25)] flex items-center gap-2 transition-colors\"\n                  >\n                    <span>{activeStep === 3 ? \"Compile SOW Outline\" : \"Next Gate\"}</span>\n                    <svg className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\">\n                      <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" strokeWidth={2.5} d=\"M9 5l7 7-7 7\" />\n                    </svg>\n                  </button>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          {/* RIGHT COL: LIVE BLUEPRINT OUTLINE PREVIEW PANEL */}\n          <div className=\"lg:col-span-5\">\n            <div className=\"bg-[#030305]/95 border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-6 font-mono relative overflow-hidden backdrop-blur-xl\">\n              {/* Abstract Blueprint Grid background */}\n              <div className=\"absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.015)_1px,transparent_1px)] [background-size:16px_16px] pointer-events-none\" />\n              \n              <div className=\"border-b border-white/5 pb-3 mb-4 flex justify-between items-center relative z-10\">\n                <span className=\"text-[10px] font-bold text-[#00FF9D] tracking-widest flex items-center gap-1.5\">\n                  <span className=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#00FF9D] animate-ping\" />\n                  LIVE BLUEPRINT SPEC DRAFT\n                </span>\n                <span className=\"text-[8px] text-white/30\">V.3.14-REV</span>\n              </div>\n\n              {/* Dynamic Draft Summary Panel */}\n              <div className=\"space-y-4 relative z-10\">\n                <div className=\"space-y-2 p-3 bg-white/[0.01] border border-white/5 rounded-xl text-xs\">\n                  <div className=\"flex justify-between text-[10px] border-b border-white/[0.03] pb-1.5\">\n                    <span className=\"text-white/40\">ORGANIZATION:</span>\n                    <span className=\"font-bold text-white truncate max-w-[150px]\">\n                      {data.organizationName || \"Sovereign Enterprise\"}\n                    </span>\n                  </div>\n                  \n                  <div className=\"flex justify-between text-[10px] border-b border-white/[0.03] pb-1.5\">\n                    <span className=\"text-white/40\">CORE INDUSTRY:</span>\n                    <span className=\"font-bold text-[#009DFF]\">\n                      {data.industry ? INDUSTRIES.find(i => i.id === data.industry)?.title : \"AWAITING SELECTION\"}\n                    </span>\n                  </div>\n\n                  <div className=\"flex justify-between text-[10px] border-b border-white/[0.03] pb-1.5\">\n                    <span className=\"text-white/40\">COMPANY SCALE:</span>\n                    <span className=\"font-bold text-white uppercase\">\n                      {data.companySize ? COMPANY_SIZES.find(c => c.id === data.companySize)?.title : \"AWAITING\"}\n                    </span>\n                  </div>\n\n                  <div className=\"flex justify-between text-[10px] border-b border-white/[0.03] pb-1.5\">\n                    <span className=\"text-white/40\">GEOGRAPHY ZONE:</span>\n                    <span className=\"font-bold text-white uppercase\">\n                      {data.geography ? GEOGRAPHIES.find(g => g.id === data.geography)?.title : \"OPTIONAL DEFAULT\"}\n                    </span>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n                {/* SOW Outline Generation Tree */}\n                <div className=\"space-y-2\">\n                  <span className=\"text-[9px] text-white/30 uppercase tracking-wider block\">Real-time SOW Section Markers:</span>\n                  \n                  <div className=\"space-y-1.5 pl-2 border-l border-white/5\">\n                    <div className=\"text-[10px] flex items-center gap-2 text-white/80\">\n                      <span className=\"text-[#009DFF] font-bold\">I.</span>\n                      <span className=\"font-bold\">EXECUTIVE STRATEGY BRIEFING</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div className=\"text-[9px] text-white/45 pl-4 italic\">\n                      {data.industry === \"healthcare\" \n                        ? \"→ Secure patient telemetry data-flow and clinical pipeline design guidelines\" \n                        : data.industry === \"banking\" \n                        ? \"→ Strategic banking consensus auditing and multi-agent fraud mitigation targets\" \n                        : \"→ High-velocity autonomous systems roadmap targeted to corporate core challenges\"}\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div className=\"text-[10px] flex items-center gap-2 text-white/80\">\n                      <span className=\"text-[#009DFF] font-bold\">II.</span>\n                      <span className=\"font-bold\">ENVIRONMENT STACK SPEC</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div className=\"text-[9px] text-white/45 pl-4\">\n                      <span>Scale Node: </span>\n                      <span className=\"text-[#00FF9D] font-bold\">\n                        {data.companySize === \"conglomerate\" ? \"Sovereign Multi-Region VPC\" : data.companySize === \"enterprise\" ? \"Single-Tenant VPC Enclave\" : \"Localized Edge Node Enclave\"}\n                      </span>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div className=\"text-[10px] flex items-center gap-2 text-white/80\">\n                      <span className=\"text-[#009DFF] font-bold\">III.</span>\n                      <span className=\"font-bold\">ENGAGEMENT MODEL SLA</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div className=\"text-[9px] text-white/45 pl-4\">\n                      {data.preferredEngagementPath ? (\n                        <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                          <span className=\"font-bold text-white uppercase block\">\n                            → {data.preferredEngagementPath} Path\n                          </span>\n                          <span className=\"text-white/40 block\">\n                            Duration: {ENGAGEMENT_PATHS.find(p => p.id === data.preferredEngagementPath)?.duration}\n                          </span>\n                        </div>\n                      ) : (\n                        <span className=\"text-white/20 italic\">Awaiting Engagement Path Selection...</span>\n                      )}\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div className=\"text-[10px] flex items-center gap-2 text-white/80\">\n                      <span className=\"text-[#009DFF] font-bold\">IV.</span>\n                      <span className=\"font-bold\">COMMERCIAL ALLOCATION</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div className=\"text-[9px] text-white/45 pl-4\">\n                      {data.budgetRange ? (\n                        <span>Budget Tier: <span className=\"text-[#00FF9D] font-bold\">{BUDGETS.find(b => b.id === data.budgetRange)?.title}</span></span>\n                      ) : (\n                        <span className=\"text-white/20\">Default strategic licensing calculations.</span>\n                      )}\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n                {/* Checklist validation markers */}\n                <div className=\"pt-3 border-t border-white/5 space-y-2\">\n                  <span className=\"text-[9px] text-white/30 uppercase tracking-wider block\">Intake Verification Status:</span>\n                  <div className=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 text-[9px]\">\n                    <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\">\n                      <span className={`w-3.5 h-3.5 rounded flex items-center justify-center font-bold ${\n                        data.industry && data.companySize ? \"bg-[#00FF9D]/10 text-[#00FF9D]\" : \"bg-white/5 text-white/20\"\n                      }`}>\n                        {data.industry && data.companySize ? \"✓\" : \"•\"}\n                      </span>\n                      <span className={data.industry && data.companySize ? \"text-white/80\" : \"text-white/30\"}>Scale Profile</span>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\">\n                      <span className={`w-3.5 h-3.5 rounded flex items-center justify-center font-bold ${\n                        data.primaryChallenge && data.priorityOutcomes.length > 0 ? \"bg-[#00FF9D]/10 text-[#00FF9D]\" : \"bg-white/5 text-white/20\"\n                      }`}>\n                        {data.primaryChallenge && data.priorityOutcomes.length > 0 ? \"✓\" : \"•\"}\n                      </span>\n                      <span className={data.primaryChallenge && data.priorityOutcomes.length > 0 ? \"text-white/80\" : \"text-white/30\"}>Challenge Matrix</span>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\">\n                      <span className={`w-3.5 h-3.5 rounded flex items-center justify-center font-bold ${\n                        data.preferredEngagementPath && data.targetTimeline ? \"bg-[#00FF9D]/10 text-[#00FF9D]\" : \"bg-white/5 text-white/20\"\n                      }`}>\n                        {data.preferredEngagementPath && data.targetTimeline ? \"✓\" : \"•\"}\n                      </span>\n                      <span className={data.preferredEngagementPath && data.targetTimeline ? \"text-white/80\" : \"text-white/30\"}>Strategy Model</span>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\">\n                      <span className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 rounded bg-[#00FF9D]/10 text-[#00FF9D] flex items-center justify-center font-bold\">\n                        ✓\n                      </span>\n                      <span className=\"text-white/80\">VPC Containment</span>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n                {/* Bottom compliance seal */}\n                <div className=\"mt-4 pt-3 border-t border-white/5 flex items-center justify-between text-[8px] text-white/30\">\n                  <span>SECURE SINGLE-TENANT BUFFER</span>\n                  <span>SHA-256 ENCRYPTED IN VRAM</span>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      )}\n\n      {/* ------------------------------------------------------------------\n          STATE 2: COMPILING ANIMATION\n          ------------------------------------------------------------------ */}\n      {appState === \"compiling\" && (\n        <div className=\"max-w-3xl mx-auto py-12\">\n          <div className=\"bg-[#030306]/95 border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8 font-mono space-y-6 relative overflow-hidden shadow-2xl\">\n            <div className=\"absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#009DFF] via-[#9D00FF] to-[#00FF9D] animate-pulse\" />\n            \n            <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between text-[10px] text-white/40 border-b border-white/5 pb-4\">\n              <span className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n                <span className=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#009DFF] animate-ping\" />\n                GFF SECURE COMPILER ACTIVE\n              </span>\n              <span>GATE COMPILATION BUFFER</span>\n            </div>\n\n            {/* Rotating radar / scanning graphic */}\n            <div className=\"flex justify-center py-6\">\n              <div className=\"relative w-28 h-28 border border-[#009DFF]/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center\">\n                <div className=\"absolute inset-0 border border-t-[#00FF9D] rounded-full animate-spin\" />\n                <div className=\"absolute inset-2 border border-[#9D00FF]/30 rounded-full\" />\n                <div className=\"w-12 h-12 bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center\">\n                  <svg className=\"w-5 h-5 text-[#009DFF] animate-pulse\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\">\n                    <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" strokeWidth={1.5} d=\"M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z\" />\n                  </svg>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n            {/* Terminal console logs */}\n            <div className=\"bg-black/40 border border-white/5 rounded-xl p-4 min-h-[160px] text-[11px] leading-relaxed text-white/70 space-y-1.5 max-h-72 overflow-y-auto\">\n              {COMPILING_LOGS.slice(0, compilingLogIndex).map((log, idx) => (\n                <div key={idx} className=\"flex gap-2\">\n                  <span className=\"text-[#00FF9D]\">✓</span>\n                  <span className=\"text-white/30\">[{idx * 0.4}s]</span>\n                  <span>{log.text}</span>\n                </div>\n              ))}\n              {compilingLogIndex < COMPILING_LOGS.length && (\n                <div className=\"flex gap-2 text-[#009DFF] animate-pulse\">\n                  <span>→</span>\n                  <span>[Executing...]</span>\n                  <span>{COMPILING_LOGS[compilingLogIndex].text}</span>\n                </div>\n              )}\n            </div>\n\n            <div className=\"text-center text-[9px] text-white/30 uppercase tracking-widest\">\n              Securing network paths • Sovereign compliance locking enforced\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      )}\n\n      {/* ------------------------------------------------------------------\n          STATE 3: COMPILED OUTLINE ARCHITECTURE FILE VIEW\n          ------------------------------------------------------------------ */}\n      {appState === \"completed\" && compiledResult && (\n        <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-start animate-fadeIn\">\n          \n          {/* LEFT COL: THE COMPILED CONTRACT FOLDER */}\n          <div className=\"lg:col-span-8 space-y-6\">\n            <div className=\"bg-[#030306]/90 border border-white/5 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden backdrop-blur-xl\">\n              \n              {/* Document Header Panel */}\n              <div className=\"p-6 md:p-8 bg-white/[0.01] border-b border-white/5 flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center justify-between gap-4\">\n                <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                  <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n                    <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono font-bold tracking-widest uppercase px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-[#00FF9D]/10 text-[#00FF9D] border border-[#00FF9D]/20\">\n                      SECURE PROPOSAL GENERATED\n                    </span>\n                    <span className=\"text-white/30 text-[9px] font-mono\">{compiledResult.revisionId}</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <h2 className=\"text-lg md:text-xl font-black text-white tracking-tight\">\n                    {data.organizationName || \"Sovereign Enterprise\"} – AI Roadmap Blueprint\n                  </h2>\n                </div>\n                <div className=\"text-right font-mono text-[9px] text-white/40\">\n                  <p>COMPILED: {compiledResult.compiledAt}</p>\n                  <p className=\"text-white/20 mt-0.5 truncate max-w-[200px]\">{compiledResult.hash}</p>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n              {/* Document Navigation Tabs */}\n              <div className=\"flex border-b border-white/5 bg-black/20 text-xs font-mono\">\n                <button\n                  type=\"button\"\n                  onClick={() => setActiveTab(\"summary\")}\n                  className={`flex-1 py-3 text-center transition-colors border-b-2 font-bold ${\n                    activeTab === \"summary\" \n                      ? \"border-[#009DFF] text-white bg-white/[0.01]\" \n                      : \"border-transparent text-white/45 hover:text-white/75\"\n                  }`}\n                >\n                  1. STRATEGY ALIGNMENT\n                </button>\n                <button\n                  type=\"button\"\n                  onClick={() => setActiveTab(\"topology\")}\n                  className={`flex-1 py-3 text-center transition-colors border-b-2 font-bold ${\n                    activeTab === \"topology\" \n                      ? \"border-[#9D00FF] text-white bg-white/[0.01]\" \n                      : \"border-transparent text-white/45 hover:text-white/75\"\n                  }`}\n                >\n                  2. ARCHITECTURE TOPOLOGY\n                </button>\n                <button\n                  type=\"button\"\n                  onClick={() => setActiveTab(\"sow\")}\n                  className={`flex-1 py-3 text-center transition-colors border-b-2 font-bold ${\n                    activeTab === \"sow\" \n                      ? \"border-[#00FF9D] text-white bg-white/[0.01]\" \n                      : \"border-transparent text-white/45 hover:text-white/75\"\n                  }`}\n                >\n                  3. DETAILED SOW SPEC\n                </button>\n                <button\n                  type=\"button\"\n                  onClick={() => setActiveTab(\"commercials\")}\n                  className={`flex-1 py-3 text-center transition-colors border-b-2 font-bold ${\n                    activeTab === \"commercials\" \n                      ? \"border-[#E4000F] text-white bg-white/[0.01]\" \n                      : \"border-transparent text-white/45 hover:text-white/75\"\n                  }`}\n                >\n                  4. COMMERCIALS & SLA\n                </button>\n              </div>\n\n              {/* TAB 1: STRATEGY ALIGNMENT */}\n              {activeTab === \"summary\" && (\n                <div className=\"p-6 md:p-8 space-y-6 animate-fadeIn\">\n                  <div className=\"space-y-4\">\n                    <h3 className=\"text-xs font-mono uppercase text-[#009DFF]\">I. Executive Alignment Strategy</h3>\n                    <p className=\"text-sm text-white/80 leading-relaxed font-light\">\n                      This sovereign deployment blueprint establishes a highly customized, dedicated network enclave optimized for{\" \"}\n                      <span className=\"text-white font-bold\">{INDUSTRIES.find(i => i.id === data.industry)?.title}</span> workflows.\n                      By isolating core data models inside a single-tenant environment, GFF resolves the fundamental conflict between enterprise security boundaries and high-efficiency intelligence.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n\n                  {/* Primary Challenge Resolution Cards */}\n                  <div className=\"p-5 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.005] space-y-4\">\n                    <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n                      <span className=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#E4000F]\" />\n                      <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase\">Primary Challenge Ingested:</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div>\n                      <h4 className=\"text-sm font-bold text-white\">\n                        {CHALLENGES.find(c => c.id === data.primaryChallenge)?.title}\n                      </h4>\n                      <p className=\"text-xs text-white/45 mt-1 leading-relaxed\">\n                        {CHALLENGES.find(c => c.id === data.primaryChallenge)?.desc}\n                      </p>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div className=\"pt-4 border-t border-white/5 space-y-2\">\n                      <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-[#00FF9D] uppercase tracking-wider block\">Targeted Operational Outcomes:</span>\n                      <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3 mt-1 text-xs\">\n                        {data.priorityOutcomes.map((outId) => {\n                          const outcomeObj = OUTCOMES.find(o => o.id === outId);\n                          return (\n                            <div key={outId} className=\"p-3.5 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#030304]\">\n                              <span className=\"font-bold text-white block\">{outcomeObj?.title}</span>\n                              <span className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40 block mt-1\">{outcomeObj?.desc}</span>\n                            </div>\n                          );\n                        })}\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n\n                  {/* Operational Timeline Metaphor */}\n                  <div className=\"space-y-3\">\n                    <h3 className=\"text-xs font-mono uppercase text-[#009DFF]\">II. Roadmap Milestones</h3>\n                    <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-xs font-mono\">\n                      <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#030304]\">\n                        <span className=\"text-[#009DFF] font-bold block mb-1\">M1: Infrastructure Seal</span>\n                        <span className=\"text-white/50\">Establish single-tenant VPC enclaves and telemetry boundaries.</span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#030304]\">\n                        <span className=\"text-[#9D00FF] font-bold block mb-1\">M2: DAG Optimization</span>\n                        <span className=\"text-white/50\">Load custom model weights and system connection nodes.</span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#030304]\">\n                        <span className=\"text-[#00FF9D] font-bold block mb-1\">M3: Autonomous Go-Live</span>\n                        <span className=\"text-white/50\">Authorize production run. Live telemetry stream and continuous drift guard active.</span>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              )}\n\n              {/* TAB 2: ARCHITECTURE TOPOLOGY */}\n              {activeTab === \"topology\" && (\n                <div className=\"p-6 md:p-8 space-y-6 animate-fadeIn\">\n                  <div className=\"space-y-3\">\n                    <h3 className=\"text-xs font-mono uppercase text-[#9D00FF]\">I. Dynamic Architecture Blueprint</h3>\n                    <p className=\"text-sm text-white/80 leading-relaxed font-light\">\n                      The GFF orchestrator functions completely isolated inside your private VPC boundary. Data flows through secure memory-locked channels with 0% persistent cloud logging.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n\n                  {/* Gorgeous Inline SVG Architecture Graphic */}\n                  <div className=\"p-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-[#020204] relative flex flex-col items-center justify-center min-h-[250px]\">\n                    <div className=\"absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.008)_1px,transparent_1px)] [background-size:20px_20px] pointer-events-none\" />\n                    \n                    {/* SVG Diagram representing VPC boundary and node connections */}\n                    <svg className=\"w-full max-w-lg h-44\" viewBox=\"0 0 500 180\" fill=\"none\">\n                      {/* Grid border */}\n                      <rect x=\"10\" y=\"10\" width=\"480\" height=\"160\" rx=\"10\" stroke=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.05)\" strokeWidth={1.5} strokeDasharray=\"4 4\" />\n                      \n                      {/* Enclave boxes */}\n                      <rect x=\"30\" y=\"30\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"rgba(0,157,255,0.03)\" stroke=\"#009DFF\" strokeWidth={1} />\n                      <rect x=\"350\" y=\"30\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"rgba(0,255,157,0.03)\" stroke=\"#00FF9D\" strokeWidth={1} />\n                      \n                      {/* Center Node Orchestrator */}\n                      <circle cx=\"250\" cy=\"90\" r=\"28\" fill=\"#111116\" stroke=\"#9D00FF\" strokeWidth={2} />\n                      \n                      {/* Connection lines */}\n                      <path d=\"M150 90 L222 90\" stroke=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.2)\" strokeWidth={1.5} strokeDasharray=\"2 2\" />\n                      <path d=\"M278 90 L350 90\" stroke=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.2)\" strokeWidth={1.5} strokeDasharray=\"2 2\" />\n\n                      {/* Direction indicators */}\n                      <circle cx=\"186\" cy=\"90\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#009DFF\" className=\"animate-pulse\" />\n                      <circle cx=\"314\" cy=\"90\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#00FF9D\" className=\"animate-pulse\" />\n                      \n                      {/* Text tags */}\n                      <text x=\"90\" y=\"24\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.4)\" fontSize=\"8\" fontFamily=\"monospace\" textAnchor=\"middle\">SECURE INGESTION</text>\n                      <text x=\"410\" y=\"24\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.4)\" fontSize=\"8\" fontFamily=\"monospace\" textAnchor=\"middle\">COGNITIVE FABRIC</text>\n                      <text x=\"250\" y=\"24\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.4)\" fontSize=\"8\" fontFamily=\"monospace\" textAnchor=\"middle\">SECURE ORCHESTRATOR</text>\n\n                      {/* Core values inside nodes */}\n                      <text x=\"90\" y=\"75\" fill=\"#white\" fontSize=\"9\" fontWeight=\"bold\" textAnchor=\"middle\">Legacy APIs</text>\n                      <text x=\"90\" y=\"95\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.5)\" fontSize=\"7\" fontFamily=\"monospace\" textAnchor=\"middle\">Air-Gapped Ingestion</text>\n\n                      <text x=\"410\" y=\"75\" fill=\"#white\" fontSize=\"9\" fontWeight=\"bold\" textAnchor=\"middle\">Sovereign LLMs</text>\n                      <text x=\"410\" y=\"95\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.5)\" fontSize=\"7\" fontFamily=\"monospace\" textAnchor=\"middle\">Memory-Lock Shields</text>\n\n                      <text x=\"250\" y=\"88\" fill=\"#white\" fontSize=\"8\" fontFamily=\"monospace\" fontWeight=\"bold\" textAnchor=\"middle\">GFF CORE</text>\n                      <text x=\"250\" y=\"100\" fill=\"#9D00FF\" fontSize=\"7\" fontFamily=\"monospace\" textAnchor=\"middle\">DAG v4.2</text>\n                    </svg>\n\n                    <div className=\"mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-4 text-[9px] font-mono text-white/50\">\n                      <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\">\n                        <span className=\"w-2 h-2 rounded bg-[#009DFF]\" />\n                        <span>Single-Tenant Ingress Boundary</span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\">\n                        <span className=\"w-2 h-2 rounded bg-[#9D00FF]\" />\n                        <span>Decentralized Telemetry Mesh</span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\">\n                        <span className=\"w-2 h-2 rounded bg-[#00FF9D]\" />\n                        <span>Zero-Retention Model Weights</span>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n\n                  {/* Selected Engagement details */}\n                  <div className=\"p-5 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.005] space-y-4\">\n                    <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center\">\n                      <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase\">Selected Engagement Framework:</span>\n                      <span className=\"text-xs font-mono font-bold text-white px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-white/5\">\n                        {ENGAGEMENT_PATHS.find(p => p.id === data.preferredEngagementPath)?.duration}\n                      </span>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div className=\"flex gap-4 items-start\">\n                      <div className=\"p-3 rounded-xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 mt-1 shrink-0\">\n                        {ENGAGEMENT_PATHS.find(p => p.id === data.preferredEngagementPath)?.icon}\n                      </div>\n                      <div>\n                        <h4 className=\"text-sm font-black text-white\">\n                          {ENGAGEMENT_PATHS.find(p => p.id === data.preferredEngagementPath)?.title} — {ENGAGEMENT_PATHS.find(p => p.id === data.preferredEngagementPath)?.tagline}\n                        </h4>\n                        <p className=\"text-xs text-white/45 leading-relaxed mt-1 font-light\">\n                          {ENGAGEMENT_PATHS.find(p => p.id === data.preferredEngagementPath)?.description}\n                        </p>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              )}\n\n              {/* TAB 3: DETAILED SOW SPEC */}\n              {activeTab === \"sow\" && (\n                <div className=\"p-6 md:p-8 space-y-6 animate-fadeIn\">\n                  <div className=\"space-y-3\">\n                    <h3 className=\"text-xs font-mono uppercase text-[#00FF9D]\">I. Statement of Work (SOW) Scope Spec</h3>\n                    <p className=\"text-sm text-white/80 leading-relaxed font-light\">\n                      The GFF Statement of Work establishes formal implementation parameters. Each stage requires collaborative key-sharing and telemetry validation.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n\n                  <div className=\"space-y-4\">\n                    <div className=\"p-5 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#030304] relative\">\n                      <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] uppercase font-bold absolute top-4 right-4\">PHASE 1</span>\n                      <h4 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white uppercase\">VPC Infrastructure Seal & Container Validation</h4>\n                      <ul className=\"text-xs text-white/50 space-y-2 mt-3 pl-4 list-disc font-light leading-relaxed\">\n                        <li>Provision single-tenant VPC boundaries in selected geographic zones ({data.geography ? GEOGRAPHIES.find(g => g.id === data.geography)?.title : \"North America Zone\"}).</li>\n                        <li>Install secure memory-locked containers utilizing strict zero-retention logging drivers.</li>\n                        <li>Verify compliance with regional sovereign legal constraints and GDPR boundaries.</li>\n                      </ul>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div className=\"p-5 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#030304] relative\">\n                      <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-[#9D00FF] uppercase font-bold absolute top-4 right-4\">PHASE 2</span>\n                      <h4 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white uppercase\">DAG Modeling & Legacy Integration API Bridging</h4>\n                      <ul className=\"text-xs text-white/50 space-y-2 mt-3 pl-4 list-disc font-light leading-relaxed\">\n                        <li>Inject customized GFF orchestrator agents matching the chosen industry taxonomy ({INDUSTRIES.find(i => i.id === data.industry)?.title}).</li>\n                        <li>Establish low-latency bridges to ingest legacy operational tables to mitigate primary lag issues.</li>\n                        <li>Configure isolated vector grids containing encrypted domain schemas and weights.</li>\n                      </ul>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div className=\"p-5 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#030304] relative\">\n                      <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-[#00FF9D] uppercase font-bold absolute top-4 right-4\">PHASE 3</span>\n                      <h4 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white uppercase\">Autonomous Promotion, Guardrails & SLA Signing</h4>\n                      <ul className=\"text-xs text-white/50 space-y-2 mt-3 pl-4 list-disc font-light leading-relaxed\">\n                        <li>Lock localized model weights and establish cryptographically sealed audit guards.</li>\n                        <li>Perform extensive drift defense penetration testing and execution audits.</li>\n                        <li>Activate production run with live telemetry logging and dedicated governance interfaces.</li>\n                      </ul>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              )}\n\n              {/* TAB 4: COMMERCIALS & SLA */}\n              {activeTab === \"commercials\" && (\n                <div className=\"p-6 md:p-8 space-y-6 animate-fadeIn\">\n                  <div className=\"space-y-3\">\n                    <h3 className=\"text-xs font-mono uppercase text-[#E4000F]\">I. Commercial Model & Licensing</h3>\n                    <p className=\"text-sm text-white/80 leading-relaxed font-light\">\n                      Financial allocation calculates core hardware licensing model parameters, estimated engineering velocity, and Day-2 maintenance schedules.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n\n                  {/* Financial & Licensing Overview Panel */}\n                  <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n                    <div className=\"p-5 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#030304] space-y-1\">\n                      <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/35 uppercase\">Estimated Implementation Term</span>\n                      <p className=\"text-lg font-bold text-white\">\n                        {data.preferredEngagementPath === \"Garage\" ? \"4 Weeks (Accelerated)\" : data.preferredEngagementPath === \"Foundry\" ? \"8 - 12 Weeks\" : data.preferredEngagementPath === \"Factory\" ? \"12 - 16 Weeks\" : \"Strategic Roadmap\"}\n                      </p>\n                      <p className=\"text-[10px] text-[#009DFF] font-mono\">Guaranteed Delivery Milestones</p>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div className=\"p-5 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#030304] space-y-1\">\n                      <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/35 uppercase\">Calculated Licensing Allocation</span>\n                      <p className=\"text-lg font-bold text-[#00FF9D]\">{compiledResult.estimatedCost}</p>\n                      <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/35 font-mono\">Annually recurring VPC instance license</p>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n\n                  {/* SLA Guarantee Panel */}\n                  <div className=\"p-5 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01] space-y-3\">\n                    <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-mono\">\n                      <svg className=\"w-4 h-4 text-[#E4000F]\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\">\n                        <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" strokeWidth={2} d=\"M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z\" />\n                      </svg>\n                      <span className=\"text-white font-bold uppercase\">Sovereign Performance SLA Guarantee</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <p className=\"text-xs text-white/50 leading-relaxed font-light\">\n                      Each deployment is governed by the cryptographically monitored GFF SLA framework. GFF guarantees <span className=\"text-white font-bold\">{compiledResult.slaGuarantee}</span>. Proactive system compliance watchdogs enforce strict regulatory containment boundaries across all operational runtimes.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              )}\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          {/* RIGHT COL: ACTION HUB / ARTIFACT BUNDLES */}\n          <div className=\"lg:col-span-4 space-y-6\">\n            <div className=\"bg-[#030305]/95 border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-6 relative overflow-hidden backdrop-blur-xl\">\n              <div className=\"border-b border-white/5 pb-3 mb-4\">\n                <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase font-bold\">Compiled SOW Blueprint Bundles</span>\n              </div>\n\n              {/* Cards represent compiled artifacts */}\n              <div className=\"space-y-4\">\n                {[\n                  { id: \"sow\", label: \"Statement of Work (SOW)\", desc: \"Legal operational SLA enclaves framework.\", filename: \"SOW_Sovereign_Draft.pdf\", color: \"#009DFF\" },\n                  { id: \"ppt\", label: \"Executive Strategy Deck\", desc: \"Board-ready alignment slides detailing ROI.\", filename: \"Board_Alignment_Sovereign.pptx\", color: \"#9D00FF\" },\n                  { id: \"schema\", label: \"Architecture Topology Spec\", desc: \"Hardened JSON DAG node routing configurations.\", filename: \"Topology_Specs.json\", color: \"#00FF9D\" }\n                ].map((artifact) => {\n                  const progress = downloadProgress[artifact.filename];\n                  const isDone = downloadSuccess[artifact.filename];\n                  \n                  return (\n                    <div\n                      key={artifact.id}\n                      className=\"p-4.5 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#030304]/80 flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[160px] relative overflow-hidden group hover:border-white/10 transition-colors\"\n                    >\n                      <div className=\"space-y-1.5 relative z-10\">\n                        <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono uppercase px-2 py-0.5 rounded tracking-wider\" style={{ color: artifact.color, backgroundColor: `${artifact.color}10`, border: `1px solid ${artifact.color}20` }}>\n                          COMPILED & READY\n                        </span>\n                        <h4 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white mt-1\">{artifact.label}</h4>\n                        <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/45 font-light leading-normal\">{artifact.desc}</p>\n                      </div>\n\n                      <div className=\"mt-4 pt-3 border-t border-white/5 relative z-10 space-y-3\">\n                        {progress !== undefined && !isDone && (\n                          <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                            <div className=\"flex justify-between text-[8px] font-mono text-white/45\">\n                              <span>ENCRYPTING PROTOCOLS...</span>\n                              <span>{progress}%</span>\n                            </div>\n                            <div className=\"w-full h-1 bg-white/5 rounded-full overflow-hidden\">\n                              <div className=\"h-full bg-[#009DFF] transition-all duration-200\" style={{ width: `${progress}%` }} />\n                            </div>\n                          </div>\n                        )}\n\n                        {isDone && (\n                          <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[9px] font-mono text-[#00FF9D] font-bold uppercase py-1\">\n                            <span>✓</span>\n                            <span>Downloaded successfully</span>\n                          </div>\n                        )}\n\n                        {progress === undefined && (\n                          <button\n                            type=\"button\"\n                            onClick={() => triggerDownload(artifact.filename)}\n                            className=\"w-full h-8 rounded text-[10px] font-bold text-white bg-white/5 border border-white/10 hover:bg-white/10 hover:border-white/25 transition-all font-mono uppercase\"\n                          >\n                            Simulate Export\n                          </button>\n                        )}\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  );\n                })}\n              </div>\n\n              {/* Bottom return to design option */}\n              <div className=\"mt-6 pt-4 border-t border-white/5 flex flex-col gap-3\">\n                <button\n                  type=\"button\"\n                  onClick={handleReset}\n                  className=\"w-full h-9 rounded-lg border border-white/10 hover:bg-white/5 text-xs text-white font-mono uppercase tracking-wider transition-colors\"\n                >\n                  Reconfigure Parameters\n                </button>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n            \n            {/* Custom security compliance callout card */}\n            <div className=\"p-5 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-[#030305]/90 relative overflow-hidden backdrop-blur-xl\">\n              <div className=\"absolute top-0 right-0 w-24 h-24 bg-[#E4000F]/2 pointer-events-none blur-xl rounded-full\" />\n              <div className=\"space-y-2.5\">\n                <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-[#E4000F] uppercase tracking-widest font-black block\">SECURITY BOUNDARY ENFORCED</span>\n                <h4 className=\"text-xs font-black text-white\">100% On-Prem & VPC Guarantee</h4>\n                <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/50 leading-relaxed font-light\">\n                  This Proposal Studio operates completely on transient browser state. GFF AI does not store, forward, or process any details entered here outside of your active browser session. Single-tenant security boundaries are programmatically certified.\n                </p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      )}\n\n      {/* ----------------- CORE CTA / FOOTER DECORATION ----------------- */}\n      <div className=\"mt-16\">\n        <ToolCTA />\n      </div>\n    </ToolPageShell>\n  );\n}\n"}}}
